title: Eritrean Dies in Israel Bus Station Attack
text:
JERUSALEMâ€”An Israeli hospital official says an Eritrean migrant shot during an attack on a bus station has died of his wounds.
Soroka Hospital spokeswoman Sharon Edri said the migrant died of his wounds late Sunday. Israeli officials say an Israeli soldier was also killed and several others hurt in the attack carried out by an Arab attacker armed with a gun and knife.
